This application demonstrates the basic kafka operation where we use post to produce a 
message which gets consumed automatically and returns the response in the log in the 
eclipse console

First start the zookeepr using cmd from the kafka location inside D:/kafka/bin/windows

cmd for zookeeper-server-start.bat ../../config/zookeeper.properties
cmd for kafka-server-start.bat ../../config/server.properties


Postman example url

POST http://localhost:9000/kafka/publish?message="sankar"
